                  <container id="aspace_ref38_c2" localtype="folder" parent="aspace_ref38_c1">17</container>
               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_eae588fc73a0d2740f76a12dcbd31f18">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Concerning finances of the late campaigns of the War of Austrian Succession. Mentioning the "Spirit of Riot and Confusion" in Holland, he scoffs at this in the first letter; later he learns that the Prince of Orange has been detained by magistrates in Amsterdam.</p>
               </scopecontent>
