               <scopecontent id="aspace_3085d767f6c197672e8d8c6426d61d73">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Requests the continuance of correspondence from Hunter. Informs him that Maj. General Huske is to take command of a certain group of troops in Holland. He is to receive credit from Hunter, as deputy paymaster.</p>
